OL,3,CParents threaten to leave island in
OL,4,Ccase of school closure
OL,6,FParents of children in Herm say they
OL,7,Fwill leave the island if the school
OL,8,Fcloses once more.
OL,10,FThe primary school is the only one on
OL,11,Fthe small island, serving a population
OL,12,Fof around 60 people and their families.
OL,14,FGuernsey's Education Committee shut
OL,15,Fdown the school in April 2023 due to a
OL,16,Flack of financial viability.
OL,18,FHowever, after dissent from islanders
OL,19,Fand other Guernsey politicians, it was
OL,20,Fre-opened four months later.
