OL,3,CParents threaten to leave island in
OL,4,Ccase of school closure
OL,6,FParents in Herm say that if it should
OL,7,Fclose again, they'd be forced to leave
OL,8,Fthe island.
OL,10,FCallum Page, Herm's engineer, says:
OL,11,F"If it happens - the school closure -
OL,12,Fthen we'll leave in September 2026.
OL,14,F"We're here to raise a family with a
OL,15,Fschool and without a school, we'll be
OL,16,Fgone".
