OL,3,CParents threaten to leave island in
OL,4,Ccase of school closure
OL,6,FParents say the school's closure would
OL,7,Fchange the island's working
OL,8,Fdemographic entirely.
OL,10,FHerm parent Fiona Hastings says: "I'd
OL,11,Fnot have come if I thought there was
OL,12,Fnot a school for them to go to. If the
OL,13,Fchildren have to commute (to Guernsey)
OL,14,Fit wouldn't be something that we would
OL,15,Fconsider.
OL,17,F"If we lose the school, families will
OL,18,Fnot come and you'll end up with a
OL,19,Fdifferent type of workforce here".
